---
title: "Street Cart" Chicken & Rice Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: This street cart-inspired dish comes together with minimal prep and a breezy cleanup, thanks to our oven-ready trays. You’ll combine chicken with a blend of shawarma-style spices and rice, dot with butter, and pop right in the oven. Serve the chicken and rice with two sauces (street-cart style!) and a green salad—then simply toss the trays!
